Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.alb.controller_nodes

Class ControllerNodesFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.alb.controller_nodes.ControllerNodesFactory
  • public class ControllerNodesFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    ControllerNodesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.alb.controller_nodes package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
